  "title": "Emergency Medical Technician & Care Assistant #SGUnitedJobs",
  "description": "<p>EMT Role</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Transport residents from the nursing home for their routine medical appointments and admission/discharge</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with the Staff Nurses in the planning of the route and time of transport.</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and working condition of the van.</li>\n  <li>Attends to any other delivery requirements or errands when needed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Care Assistant Role</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assists the registered nurses in the delivery of nursing care to the residents in the Home.</li>\n  <li>Assists the physiotherapist in the delivery of therapeutic activities to the residents in the Home</li>\n  <li>Helps to maintain a clean, safe and neat environment for the residents in the nursing home.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Relevant EMT course with SCDF/SAF</li>\n  <li>AED/BCLS Certified</li>\n  <li>Able to work under high pressure and fast pace environment</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Successful applicants without the qualifications will be sent for Certificate in Community Care (Community Care Traineeship Programme) with all courses funded by the employer.</p>",
